{"tid":2067373,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得滿月之戰好Underrated [多GIF圖][手機用戶注意]","createTime":"2020-06-17T03:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T03:05:01.000Z","uid":253574,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b9f423b33d815576ae94bd2949bbae1c6ff75fa9","tid":2067373,"uid":253574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"本身都係覺得 又係啲咩<br />\n魔法少女 賣下萌 搞下百合咁<br />\n但見佢有tag機戰 就睇下咁<br />\n點知真係比我預期中好好多 <br />\n每集啲劇情都吸引我睇落去<br />\n作為原創動畫 幾驚佢得個頭無尾<br />\n例如 Darling乜乜 笑容代價咁<br />\n<br />\n咁故事內容就基本上係 <br />\n用機械人戰鬥嘅魔法少女 <br />\n為左實現願望而參加聖杯戰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uh9iusP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuh9iusP.gif&h=282107a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ruGg0zx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FruGg0zx.gif&h=df69117d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gz9ZdUC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGz9ZdUC.gif&h=ccf99e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FEBEdUF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFEBEdUF.gif&h=51c95cf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLSgf9y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLSgf9y.gif&h=f9fd4ca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9xW0Bf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9xW0Bf.gif&h=50828320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/36nv422.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F36nv422.gif&h=3d84dfbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港嘅魔法少女代表係 風水師<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhMMDog.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhMMDog.gif&h=b5fead04&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n都幾多向高達系列致敬位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mbgkHQf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h